            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1668682878,
            "creation_date": 1668638152,
            "body": "<p>tough time omitting characters for only C<\/p>\n<pre><code>p = Pattern.compile(&quot;(?i).*\\\\bC\\\\b(?!\\\\+|#|\\\\$|\\\\*|\\\\^|%|&amp;|\\\\.).*&quot;);\n  m = p.matcher(test);\n    if(m.find()) {\n        System.out.println(&quot;C is true&quot;);\n    }\n    p = Pattern.compile(&quot;(?i).*\\\\bc\\\\+\\\\+\\\\B.*&quot;);\n  m = p.matcher(test);\n    if(m.find()) {\n        System.out.println(&quot;C++ is true&quot;);\n    }\n    p = Pattern.compile(&quot;(?i).*\\\\bc\\\\#\\\\B.*&quot;);\n  m = p.matcher(test);\n    if(m.find()) {\n        System.out.println(&quot;C# is true&quot;);\n    }\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 74468079,
